sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Click remove channel member
    Frontend->>API: DELETE /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{channelId}/members/{userId}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace, channel and target user
    DB-->>API: Data found
    API->>DB: Remove channel membership
    DB-->>API: Membership deleted
    API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
    Frontend-->>Owner: Refresh channel members list
